body:

## Problem

Let $X$ have a probability density function

$$
f_X(x) =
\begin{cases}
 1/4 & 0 < x < 1 \\\
 3/8 & 3 < x < 5 \\\
 0 & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
$$

(a) Find the cumulative distribution function of $X$.

(b) Let $Y = 1/X$. Find the probability density function $f\_y(y)$ for $Y$. Hint: Consider three cases: 
- $1/5 \leq y \leq 1/3$
- $1/3 \leq y \leq 1$
- $y \geq 1$.

